<HEAD>Border Patrol Bus Runs Off Road; Eight Injured</HEAD>
<DATELINE>SAN YSIDRO, Calif. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   An Immigration and Naturalization
Service bus carrying undocumented aliens back to Mexico ran off a
highway early Sunday, slightly injuring six Mexicans and two U.S.
agents, authorities said.
   The bus, with 63 people on board, was en route from San Clemente
to the San Ysidro border crossing on Interstate 805 when the driver
